# Storage & export (v1)

## Session folder (source of truth)

Persist each recording session as a single folder under a user-visible directory:

- `audio.m4a` (always write, even if rolling transcription is enabled)
- `metadata.json` (app version, sample rate, channels, model, timestamps)
- `transcript.rolling.json` (optional, for crash recovery)
- `transcript.final.json` and `transcript.final.md`
- `notes.json` and `notes.md` (optional)

## Performance rule

- Do not write every draft update to disk.
- Use periodic checkpoints (e.g. ~60s) and on stop/pause/background.

## Integrity rule

- If audio gaps/dropped buffers are detected, insert **gap markers** into the transcript model.
- Never “smooth over” missing audio with invented text.

